There are 10 friends sitting in a circular formation. Each friend speaks a word of the sentence "The sun rises in the east". When the sentence has been spoken twice, the order reverses.
Eg:
Friend no.    Word
1             The
2			  sun
3             rises
4             in 
5             the
6             east 
7             The
8             sun
9             rises
10            in
1             the 
2             east
1             the     //Notice that the order reverses here.
10            in
9             rises 
8             sun
7             The


Print the list for 1000 iterations. Each line should contain the friend number and word he/she speaks.